Ah, GHOST. I'm not a fan of the unlicensed GHOST releases like Iced Tea
Lemonade, which I've tried but have not (yet) written on. This new Blue
Raspberry will replace [[Ghost_Energy_Sour_Patch_Kids_Blue_Raspberry]] as Ghost
lost the license to produce Nabisco-branded products following the acquisition
of 60% of stake of GHOST by Dr. Pepper Keurig.

