Blue Raspberry tastes like the Sour Patch Kids Blue Raspberry GHOST with a bit
less citric acid and with a subtle note of some fruit like an apple. Other than
that, still has the same trademark fantastic blue raspberry taste and, compared
to other non-GHOST drinks, still very sour even in its dampened state.

As with most good zero-sugar drinks this Ghost is sweetened with acesulfame
potassium and sucralose.

